==题词==
石柱的最后两个单词是（中括号中是后人的猜测<ref name=DocumentsofAGreekM1>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=jVud8Fz6wTMC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA91#v=onepage&q&f=false|editor1-first=Egert|editor1-last=Pöhlmann|editor2-first=Martin L.|editor2-last=West|title=page 91|year=2001|access-date=2014-11-03|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220094424/https://books.google.com/books?id=jVud8Fz6wTMC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA91#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>) ）：
{{quote|'''{{lang|grc|Σείκιλος Εὐτέρ[πῃ]}}''', ''Seikilos Euter[pei]'',}} 
意思是说"塞基洛斯献给艾戴佩"，也即根据这种猜测，墓碑可能是塞基洛斯为妻子艾戴佩所立。<ref name=HarvardDictionaryMusic>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=02rFSecPhEsC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA767#v=onepage&q&f=false|page=767|chapter=Seikilos epitaph|editor-first=Don Michael|editor-last=Randel|year=2003|title=|access-date=2015-12-08|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220100922/https://books.google.com/books?id=02rFSecPhEsC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA767#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
另一种可能性是
{{quote|'''{{lang|grc|Σείκιλος Εὐτέρ[που]}}''', ''Seikilos Euter[pou]'',}} 
意思是说"尤特普的塞基洛斯"，也即塞基洛斯，尤特普之子。<ref name=DocumentsofAGreekM/><ref name=DocumentsofAGreekM1/><ref>{{cite book|first=John J.|last=Pilch|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5kzYwVosDUMC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA79#v=onepage&q&f=false|year=2011|title=page 79|access-date=2014-11-03|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220100554/https://books.google.com/books?id=5kzYwVosDUMC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA79#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>
